# SAP API classification data (CSV and XML) goes here.
# Download from: https://github.com/SAP/abap-atc-cr-cv-s4hc
#
# After downloading, generate a checksum file for integrity verification:
#   cd input && sha256sum *.csv *.xml > SHA256SUMS
#
# The SHA256SUMS file IS tracked by git; the CSV/XML data files are git-ignored.
